# {{SPACE_TITLE}}

Warm vLLM Space for repeated runtime and evaluation iteration.

## Runtime

- Base image: `{{BASE_IMAGE}}`
- App port: `{{APP_PORT}}`
- Template: `vllm_warm`

## Recommended Variables

- `BASE_MODEL`: base model to serve, for example `google/gemma-4-E4B-it`
- `ADAPTER_BUCKET_URI`: optional adapter prefix, for example `hf://buckets/<bucket-id>/runs/.../final_model`
- `GPU_MEMORY_UTILIZATION`: defaults to `0.85`
- `LIMIT_MM_PER_PROMPT`: optional multimodal cap, for example `image=0 audio=0`
- `VLLM_EXTRA_ARGS`: optional shell-style extra args passed through to vLLM
- `LORA_MAX_RANK`: defaults to `64`
- `LORA_MODULE_NAME`: defaults to `finetuned`
- `VLLM_TENSOR_PARALLEL_SIZE`: optional tensor parallel size

## Recommended Persistent Cache Variables

- `HF_HOME=/data/.huggingface`
- `PIP_CACHE_DIR=/data/.cache/pip`
- `HF_HUB_ENABLE_HF_TRANSFER=1`

## Notes

- This Space is intended for warm iteration, not canonical experiment records.
- Pause the Space when idle to avoid paying for unused GPU time.
- Keep final tracked train/eval artifacts on HF Jobs.
